      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.archetypes.Item.S8O1OZvahGgiY5Kr]{Battleflower}</p>\n<p>As part of a move action, you can expend 1 Resolve Point to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.HWJ570MVgFoO5Reb#take-20]{take 20} on an @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.3QdtsfnVJsHEdrt0]{Acrobatics} check to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.3QdtsfnVJsHEdrt0#balance]{balance}, or 2 Resolve Points to take 20 on an Acrobatics check to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.3QdtsfnVJsHEdrt0#tumble]{tumble}. For balance, the effect lasts up to 1 minute, and for tumble, it lasts 1 round. In both cases, you can move at full speed.</p>"
